Organization Name: JOHNSON COUNTY FAMILY CRISIS CENTER | CRISIS CENTER | DOMESTIC VIOLENCE AND SEXUAL ASSAULT SERVICES
Description: Provides shelter, counseling and support groups for primary and secondary victims of family violence and/or sexual assault.

Organization Name: FORT WORTH VET CENTER | FORT WORTH SITE | VETERANS SERVICES
Description: Provides outpatient psychological counseling including: Individual and group counseling for Veterans, service members, and their families Family counseling for military related issues Bereavement (grief) counseling Military sexual trauma counseling and referral Community outreach and education Substance abuse assessment and referral Employment referral Referral of other VA services

Organization Name: WOMENS CENTER OF TARRANT COUNTY, THE | FORT WORTH OFFICE | VICTIM SERVICES
Description: Offers trauma-informed counseling to survivors who have experienced sexual assault. Offers supportive services such as sexual assault exam support, legal services, and criminal justice accompaniment.
